Use the _[printf](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/io/PrintStream.html#printf(java.lang.String,java.lang.Object...))_ method.\
The _[Formatter](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/util/Formatter.html)_ class _JavaDoc_ has a list of _format-specifiers_ and other _syntax_.

```java
System.out.printf(&quot;%5d&quot;, numbers[i]);
```

Output

```none
Array Contents:
   16  114   26   59  177   67   61  105    1  190
   22   85  123   42   67   20  189  167   69  175
  194   39  135   28   54    8   68   94  107  134
